I"A<div class="p">The rounded boulders interfere</div>
<div class="p">With the prolific stream</div>
<div class="p">That breaks upon a chandelier</div>
<div class="p">With crystals, and the gleam</div>
<div class="p">Of light is shivered from the spot</div>
<div class="p">Like violence upon a seam</div>
<div class="p">Or turbulence of thought.</div>
<p> </p>
<div class="p">The rocks are men who clash in arms,</div>
<div class="p">Substantial with a thought,</div>
<div class="p">The stream the course of Thought's alarms</div>
<div class="p">And concord; when men fought</div>
<div class="p">It mostly ran, despite attacks,</div>
<div class="p">Despite the burthen men had wrought</div>
<div class="p">And wore upon their backs.</div>
<p> </p>
<div class="p">Thus peaceful motion in the river</div>
<div class="p">Toward a precipice.</div>
<div class="p">And thus uncomprehending diver</div>
<div class="p">Merrily amiss</div>
<div class="p">Steps; when he trips, the water drops,</div>
<div class="p">And both descend the cliff,</div>
<div class="p">Then suddenly thought stops.</div>
